# iOS Development Playbook

When implementing iOS work:

- Follow single-type-per-file structure.
- Use extensions to separate concerns clearly.
- Reuse shared components and services.
- Comment public APIs, async behavior, and complex state.
- If UI design is involved, also follow the repository's admin UI quality rules.
